# Rate Limiting

- **Centralized Logic**: Use `app/core/ratelimit.py` helpers. Avoid duplicating token bucket/leaky bucket logic.
- **Status**: Maintain status endpoint(s) under `app/api/v1/status.py` with consistent schemas.
- **Headers**: When applicable, include standard rate limit headers.
- **Observability**: Emit counters for throttled requests.

